    Place(name: 'H Gonia ', imagePath: 'Limassolnight/gonia.jpg', lat: 34.67595346991435, long:33.0434779965245, category: 'Bar', id: 89, city: 'Limassol', description: 'Gonia Saripolou in Lemesos (Limassol), Cyprus, is a notable area known for its variety of dining and entertainment options. It features various restaurants and eateries that cater to different tastes, such as Magirio-Tavernaki to Laiko, which is located at the junction of Gonia Saripolou & Kanari in Limassol. Additionally, Saripolou Square is surrounded by a diverse range of food and dining establishments, including taverns, lounge bars, and restaurants offering international cuisines.This area appears to be a vibrant and lively part of Limassol, offering a mix of culinary experiences and potentially a bustling nightlife, making it a popular destination for both locals and visitors (photo from Check In Cyprus).', url: 'https://igoniacy.wixsite.com/igonia?fbclid=IwAR0Ce4tJtbVb6pxowiKpnB7yMT5CO74qvI7oYochCrY5DnetBW9kr8IGdgs'),
    Place(name: 'Guaba Beach Bar', imagePath: 'Limassolnight/guaba.jpg', lat: 34.702586504754464, long:33.10799587426309,id:91,  category: 'Beach Bar', city: 'Limassol', description: 'Guaba Beach Bar in Limassol is a vibrant and popular destination, known for its lively atmosphere and a wide range of activities and events. It offers various entertainment options such as Zumba mornings, performances by renowned DJs like Nick Warren and Nervo, and special themed parties like the UV Beach Party. The bar creates an engaging environment with its mix of music genres,Guaba Beach Bar is particularly noted for its dynamic events, which include not only musical performances but also fitness activities like Zumba, adding a unique aspect to the beach bar experience. This combination of music, dance, and fitness activities makes it a distinctive and sought-after location in Limassol for both locals and tourists.', url: 'https://guababeachbar.com') ,
    Place(name: 'Summer Breeze Bar', imagePath: 'Limassolnight/breeze.png', lat: 34.69984277962463,id: 92, long: 33.101163354239176, city: 'Limassol', category: 'Night Club', description: 'Summer Breeze Club in Limassol, Cyprus, is a notable nightlife destination known for its vibrant summer events. It is the only club in the city that\'s just a breath away from the sea, featuring an ultra-modern black and white striped design. The club is renowned for hosting international and European events, including performances by famous Greek and international artists as well as international DJs. This makes it a popular spot for unforgettable summer nights filled with entertainment and surprises.The club is distinguished for its innovative décor, impressive lighting, and state-of-the-art audio system, which are renewed every summer season. It has also been recognized internationally for its outdoor design and originality, receiving awards in London and in the "Stoli Original Bar & Club Awards." The wide range of alcoholic beverages, creative cocktails, and champagnes offered at the bar further enhances the overall experience.', url: 'https://www.breezesummer.com')
    ,Place(name: 'Bar du Soleil', imagePath: 'Limassolnight/bardu.jpg', lat: 34.670831348989275, long: 33.04296205354445, id: 93, category: 'Bar', city: 'Limassol', description:'Bar du Soleil in Limassol is a unique bar that offers an immersive experience combining luxurious aesthetics, historical ambiance, and a diverse range of signature cocktails. The bar\'s setting in the Old Port of Limassol seamlessly blends historical elements with modern design, creating an atmosphere that is both visually striking and inviting. It\'s a place where interior design transcends simple aesthetics, offering guests a journey into a world of creativity and imagination (photo from Check In Cyprus).', url: 'https://bardusoleil.com/'),
    Place(name: 'Notes Live', imagePath: 'Limassolnight/notes.jpg', lat: 34.67354189335141, long: 33.04174489100214, id: 94, city: 'Limassol', category: 'Music Venue', description: 'Notes Live in Limassol is a prominent clubbing and music venue, known for its commitment to high-quality music and entertainment. Established in 1993, Notes Live has become a significant part of the Cypriot music scene, popular for hosting and promoting top-notch music events. It has garnered attention for its excellent service, unique atmosphere, and reasonable pricing, making it a favorite among both locals and tourists.The venue has gained recognition not just in Cyprus but also in the Greek media, being recommended as a must-visit destination in Cyprus. Notes Live is known for featuring major figures from the Greek music scene and beyond, offering a diverse range of musical experiences to its visitors (photo from Check In Cyprus).', url: 'https://www.instagram.com/notes.live/'),
    Place(name: 'Ravens Music Hall', imagePath: 'Limassolnight/ravens.jpg', lat: 34.675006629422185, long: 33.043307310064165, id: 95, city: 'Limassol', category: 'Music Venue', description: 'Ravens Music Hall in Limassol is a notable venue that offers an intimate and friendly atmosphere for live music enthusiasts. Known for showcasing some of the best bands in Cyprus, it features an excellent sound system, top acoustics, and a layout that ensures the stage is visible from any seat in the house. This makes it an ideal place for those who are passionate about live music experiences.The venue operates with table service and tends to get busy, especially on weekends. To accommodate its guests comfortably and maintain its intimate ambiance, advanced booking is recommended, which can be done via phone. Ravens Music Hall hosts a wide range of genres, making it a versatile spot for different musical tastes (photo from Tripadvisor).', url: 'https://www.facebook.com/Ravens.limassol'),
    Place(name: 'Face Club',  imagePath: 'Limassolnight/face.jpg', lat: 34.67300322557885, long: 33.04154692464629, id: 6016, category: 'Night Club', city: 'Limassol', description: 'Face Club in Limassol is a nightlife spot that\'s part of the city\'s vibrant club and bar scene. It\'s known for offering a dynamic atmosphere, making it a popular choice for those looking to experience Limassol\'s nightlife. The club is usually open until the early hours of the morning, typically closing around 4:30 AM on Saturdays.While detailed information about the club\'s specific offerings, events, or unique features isn\'t readily available from the sources I accessed, Face Club\'s presence in the heart of Limassol suggests it\'s well-integrated into the local entertainment scene. Visitors to Limassol often engage in various activities like sightseeing tours, water sports, and exploring the city\'s cultural attractions. Face Club seems to fit into this diverse array of entertainment options, offering a place for both locals and tourists to enjoy the city\'s nightlife.', url: 'https://www.breezegroup.com.cy/faceclublimassol')
    ,Place(name: 'Gerrard\'s Kitchen Bar',id: 8001, imagePath: 'Limassolnight/gerrard.jpg', lat: 34.70671532263273, long: 33.118786583616426, city: 'Limassol', category: 'Pub',url: 'https://www.facebook.com/gerrardscy/', description: 'Gerrard Kitchen Bar in Limassol is a popular gastronomic destination that combines modern culinary techniques with traditional flavors, creating a delightful dining experience. This establishment is well-regarded for its innovative approach to cuisine, serving a fusion of Mediterranean dishes with global influences. Gerrard Kitchen Bar boasts a chic and contemporary interior, with a welcoming atmosphere that makes diners feel both comfortable and intrigued by the culinary delights on offer (photo from Restaurant Guru).' ),
     Place(name: 'Hustlers Rock Bar',url: 'https://www.facebook.com/hustlersrockclub/', imagePath: 'Limassolnight/hustlers.jpg',id: 1025, lat: 34.67298164350808, long: 33.043936154244676, city: 'Limassol', category: 'Bar', description: 'Hustlers Rock Bar, nestled in the heart of a bustling city, is a mythical haven for rock enthusiasts and nightlife adventurers. Imagined as an underground oasis, it features walls adorned with legendary rock memorabilia, guitars hanging from the ceiling, and a stage that has hosted the ghostly performances of rock legends. Patrons can enjoy an array of mystical drinks concocted from secret recipes passed down through generations of rock gods. The air is thick with the sounds of classic riffs and the spirit of rebellion, making it the ultimate destination for those seeking to escape the mundane and dive into a night of rock-fueled enchantment (photo from Tripadvisor).')
    ,Place(name: 'BordelloBar',url: 'https://www.breezegroup.com.cy/bordello' , imagePath: 'Limassolnight/bordellobar.jpg',id: 1026, lat: 34.67452304682347, long: 33.04475697307997, category: 'Bar', city: 'Limassol', description: 'Imagine a bar where every corner whispers tales of rock legends, Hustlers Rock Bar. Nestled in the heart of a vibrant city, this mythical venue is a sanctuary for those who live by the beat of the drums and the rifts of a guitar. With walls adorned with memorabilia of rock\'s golden years, patrons find themselves stepping into a realm where music reigns supreme. The air vibrates with the echoes of classic rock anthems, as live bands take the stage nightly, resurrecting the spirits of rock icons. Here, the drinks flow as freely as the music, each cocktail named after legendary songs, inviting guests to toast to the immortals of rock. Hustlers Rock Bar isn\'t just a bar. it\'s a time machine, a tribute, a place where the night is always young, and the music never dies (photo from Tripadvisor).'),
    Place(name: 'Marina Roof Bar',url: 'https://www.facebook.com/MarinaRoofBar/', imagePath: 'Limassolnight/marina.jpg',id: 1027, lat: 34.66878672153584, long: 33.040305515649315, city: 'Limassol', category: 'Bar', description: 'The Marina Roof Bar, located atop TGI Fridays in Limassol Marina, is a vibrant new addition to Limassol\'s nightlife. It offers a unique menu with an array of magnificent cocktails, enticing evening starters, and both local and international summer wines, all complemented by stunning views of the Limassol Marina sea. The bar\'s design, featuring white, wavy fabrics reminiscent of sea waves, along with funky music from renowned DJs, creates a special atmosphere for summer nights (photo from C+ Studio Architects).'),
    Place(name: 'Rumours Bar',url: 'https://rumourscy.com/en/', imagePath: 'Limassolnight/rumours_bg_2.jpg', lat: 34.69740071705598, long: 33.092477228770335,id: 1028, category: 'Bar', city: 'Limassol', description: 'Rumours Bar in Limassol is a vibrant and popular destination for both locals and tourists looking for a lively night out. Known for its dynamic atmosphere and friendly vibe, this bar offers a wide range of drinks, from classic cocktails to local specialties, catering to a diverse clientele. The interior is typically designed to encourage socializing, featuring comfortable seating areas, a well-stocked bar, and often, an area for live music or a DJ booth where guests can dance to the latest hits as well as timeless classics.')
  , Place(name: 'Metropole Retro Club',url: 'https://www.facebook.com/RetroMetropoleClub/', imagePath: 'Limassolnight/retro.jpg',id: 1029, lat: 34.67513017264866, long: 33.04571264749465, category: 'Night Club', city: 'Limassol',description: 'Metropole Retro Club is likely to be a nightlife venue that specializes in offering a nostalgic experience, celebrating the music, fashion, and culture of past decades. While specific details about the club could vary, venues like Metropole Retro Club typically feature decor and themes that transport patrons back in time, whether it\'s to the disco era of the 70s, the neon-lit 80s, or the dance-pop 90s (photo from All About Limassol).')
